story_teamgalactic_01_10000/2401_1201_03: Phew! That was a huge help.
story_teamgalactic_01_10000/2401_1201_04:
But why’d that grunt attack members of his
own team?
story_teamgalactic_01_10000/2401_1201_05:
To fool your enemies, you must first fool
your allies!
story_teamgalactic_01_10000/2401_1201_07: Ah! You’re that weird guy from Jubilife City!
story_teamgalactic_01_10000/2401_1201_08:
You really have a knack for saying the rudest
things, you know that?
story_teamgalactic_01_10000/2401_1201_09:
Sorry... I’m on edge from these battles with
Team Galactic.
story_teamgalactic_01_10000/2401_1201_10:
So you’re who the International Police sent to
investigate Pasio!
story_teamgalactic_01_10000/2401_1201_11:
Sure am! Glad to team up with you on an
investigation again!
story_teamgalactic_01_10000/2401_1201_12: Hurry, we need reinforcements! Over here!
story_teamgalactic_01_10000/2401_1201_13: Looks like they’re calling for backup.
story_teamgalactic_01_10000/2401_1201_14: Go on, leave this to me.
story_teamgalactic_01_10000/2401_1201_15:
No time to lose. Keep heading deeper into
the hideout!
